                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10011" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0628</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">425 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">F公司企业文化如何赋分又赋能？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How does Company F’s culture assign scores and enhance capabilities?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张雪娇，戴凌，陈思楠，陈炘，赵青扬，乔玉洋</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京林业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">F公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源管理；企业文化；赋分制；国企专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Human resources management; Corporate culture; Bonus scoring system</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源管理是提升企业竞争力的关键，企业文化是影响让人力资源管理的重要因素，优秀的企业文化可以通过凝聚力、导向力、激励力等协同企业和员工的目标，进而促进员工成长并推动企业战略目标的实现。本案例聚焦F公司的“赋分制”管理改革，介绍了F公司如何汲取企业文化的力量来激发公司管理潜能的过程，复现了F公司在改革过程中是如何在内外因素的驱动下释放改革动能、在复合人才追求的背景下挖掘核心技能、在文化小组的组建下落地工作效能、在现有员工培养体系下对接双轨才能以及在总结改革成果下激发改革潜能的过程。本案例从企业文化视角描述F公司顺利开展赋分制改革的成功经历，旨在帮助学员理解和掌握如何通过企业文化赋能人力资源管理，引导学员思考如何让企业文化真正落地生根，促进企业高质量发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Human resources management is the key to enhancing corporate competitiveness, and corporate culture is an important factor influencing human resources management. An excellent corporate culture can synergize the goals of the company and its employees through cohesion, guidance, and motivation, thereby promoting employee growth and driving the realization of corporate strategic objectives. This case study focuses on the “Points System” performance management reform of Company F, detailing how Company F harnessed the power of corporate culture to stimulate management potential. It illustrates how Company F released reform momentum driven by internal and external factors during the reform process, explored core skills amidst the pursuit of composite talents, implemented work efficiency through the establishment of cultural groups, aligned dual-track talents within the existing employee training system, and stimulated reform potential through summarizing reform outcomes. This case describes the successful experience of Company F in carrying out the Points System reform from the perspective of corporate culture, aiming to help learners understand and master how to empower human resources management through corporate culture, and guide them to consider how to make corporate culture take root and promote firms’ high-quality development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ARDM模型框架；胜任力素质模型的转换；职位分析流程；职业生涯规划与管理；员工关系管理工作方法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-10</td>
                            </tr>
